snippet.textDisplay: Hi Ana. It’s so lovely to see how appreciative Atticus is of his gifts, bless his heart. As a mum myself, I want to say that you and your mum do an amazing job. Just a little question that I hope is okay; I have an 8 year old little boy who is autistic (and two babies), he doesn’t like any toys or presents so we always buy for the local toy donations instead at Christmas. My little boy loves watching you with me and we would love to send Atticus a gift after Christmas from my son. I’ll have a look out for some of the Jurassic World eggs. Would be our pleasure. Merry Christmas.xxx
